## Feature 3 Create A New Spot

# 1. Add New Spot Button in the Navigation Bar

* Make sure the button is only visible to logged-in users

# 2. Create the New Spot Form Component

* This component will collect data for the new spot

# 3.  Add Routing

* Ensure the app has routes to access the new pot form

# 4. Handle Form Submission

* Implement form validation and submission logic to handle the spot creation and navigate to the new spot's detail page upon successful creation.

# 5. Styling

* Add css to style the form and ensure it matches the wireframe layout